Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:25.30,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}In spite of how the world decides to see my life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:29.53,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Would I still have a chance for us to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:35.82,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:43.30,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fad(400,400)}If I decide to burn instead of fading out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:47.30,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fad(400,400)}I still would like the chance for us to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:54.68,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fad(400,400)}Over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:59.20,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}If we can be found, we sure can get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:03.64,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}Through all the madness of falling in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:12.08,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fad(200,400)}If we're truly lost, I don't want to be found here dying alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:17.22,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fad(400,400)}The stain of RED that colors the pavement
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:21.18,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fad(400,400)}Painted with blood of somebody you love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:26.04,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fad(400,400)}Is this sacrifice for the broken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:31.02,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\fad(400,600)}Losing the purest of what's in your heart
